{"tid":370060,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人願意暫養/領養狗狗","createTime":"2017-08-22T19:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T20:34:49.000Z","uid":81684,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0066e91807d015aee5d73a7668544c665ffa61f","tid":370060,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"幫朋友開post<br />\n懷疑比人專程揸車入嚟遺棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本應一公一乸恩恩愛愛仲有個仔<br />\n無奈隻爸爸比車車死咗<br />\n媽媽又比野豬咬傷 而家同個仔相依為命<br />\n兩隻都有牛蜱 唔識流浪 好乖 好嗲人 唔吠<br />\n我可以出醫療費 但係冇地方安置佢地<br />\n已經問過好多義工同非牟利都幫唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dace176ea21ced34cd1d2da5cbf94d8bb404f607","tid":370060,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0065e9a02f5af281fd2f1111452e4f74c844ded6","tid":370060,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:53:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd5cbd33706d5d7f2af56b7023df78d3a21ab0a9","tid":370060,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:54:35.000Z","msg":"咁依家你咪要係街等？我幫手轉發下"},{"pid":"26e3a29dce1d768b68e7f3c91394f09f13cc347c","tid":370060,"uid":137929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:55:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d66e1e598788c6d473d53350604e0712c821a45","tid":370060,"uid":40560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:55:56.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0af56a20196c15f2b6f1424dd392b6040c6468","tid":370060,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地真係好得意㗎<br />\n無奈我真係冇地方<br />\n唔忍心佢地再面對失去同伴<br />\n佢地真係好有性 好錫對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696c8a5a6a394d22280502abaf3a97b7d62a9e97","tid":370060,"uid":37027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:58:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3136717144aee5e9d7af3e2ad3da814cb4f19e","tid":370060,"uid":54051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:58:50.000Z","msg":"推推推  有冇post係fb 唐狗會次類"},{"pid":"9f1bc922074c7982c807441523635a33ac7bb59d","tid":370060,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁依家你咪要係街等？我幫手轉發下</blockquote><br />\n平時有餵佢地<br />\n啱啱想跟我返屋企<br />\n我唯有跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b85ea627f3d9bd734154f84be0a22be52c37e6","tid":370060,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T20:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推推推  有冇post係fb 唐狗會次類</blockquote><br />\n有朋友周圍問過<br />\n但係唔夠傷/唔夠慘<br />\n叫返我自己搵人暫養<br />\n一係放返原地<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔識流浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bcc6ce6247e0afb9f8431a4c14919ed0bad991","tid":370060,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T20:04:39.000Z","msg":"本來兩公婆好恩愛成日互錫<br />\n當正個仔透明<br />\n而家爸爸走咗<br />\n個仔就照顧媽媽<br />\n幫佢搲痕 傍實佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e7685026956a2901cfc850601ce9215d5ce284","tid":370060,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T20:04:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6c4ffcd277f6a9f070946b6650a59b48fd73ff7","tid":370060,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T20:05:18.000Z","ms